f the irrigation event in minutes'\\n          example: 15\\n        water_used_liters:\\n          type: number\\n          format: float\\n          description: 'Amount of water used during the event in liters'\\n          example: 50\\n    SmartAgriSensorResponse:\\n      type: object\\n      description: 'Response object from smart agriculture sensor including soil moisture, weather forecast, and irrigation events'\\n      properties:\\n        soil_moisture:\\n          type: number\\n          format: float\\n          description: 'Current soil moisture percentage'\\n          example: 23.5\\n        weather_forecast:\\n          $ref: '#/components/schemas/WeatherForecast'\\n        irrigation_events:\\n          type: array\\n          description: 'List of recent automated irrigation events'\\n          items:\\n            $ref: '#/components/schemas/IrrigationEvent'\\n\"\n}"
